<div><head>《雜祭法》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.2">凡祭法，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.3">有廟者置之於座，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.4">未遑立廟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.5">祭於廳事可也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.6">《太平御覽》卷一百八十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.7">凡臨祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.8">坐以蒲薦青布練褥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.9">其事從約也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-1a.10">虞世南《北堂書鈔》卷八十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.2">香爐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.3">四時祠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.4">坐側皆置也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.5">《太平御覽》卷七百三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.6">四時之祠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.7">皆用苦酒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-2a.8">《北堂書鈔》卷一百六十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a.2">祠用白黍、黃黍。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a.3">《太平御覽》卷八百五十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a.4">四時祠皆用安乾特。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a.5">《太平御覽》卷八百五十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a.6">冬時用荊餳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-3a.7">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.2">四時皆用饊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.3">《太平御覽》卷八百五十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.4">春祠用曼頭、餳餅、髓餅、牢丸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.5">夏、秋、冬亦如之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.6">夏祠別用乳餅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.7">冬祠用白環餅。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-4a.8">徐堅《初學記》卷二十六、《太平御覽》卷八百六十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.2">四時祠皆用𦠆。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.3">《北堂書鈔》卷一百四十五。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.4">春祠用大䐑。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.5">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.6">冬祀用腊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.7">雉腊、兔腊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-5a.8">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.2">四時祠皆用肺臏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.3">《太平御覽》卷八百五十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.4">春、夏、秋祠皆用䐄血。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.5">《北堂書鈔》卷一百四十五、《太平御覽》卷八百五十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.6">春祠用脯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.7">夏用煏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-6a.8">《初學記》卷二十六、《太平御覽》卷八百六十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a.2">秋祠用菹消。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a.3">《太平御覽》卷八百五十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a.4">夏祠、秋祠皆用瓜。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a.5">《初學記》卷二十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a.6">春、秋、冬祠皆用栗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-7a.7">《藝文類聚》卷八十七、《太平御覽》卷九百六十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a.2">春祀用棗油。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a.3">《初學記》卷二十六、《太平御覽》卷九百六十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a.4">冬祠用柑。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a.5">《太平御覽》卷九百六十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a.6">夏祠用杏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-8a.7">《太平御覽》卷九百六十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-9a.2">夏祠用白㮏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-9a.3">秋時用赤㮏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-9a.4">《太平御覽》卷九百七十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-9a.5">冬祀用甘蔗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1359_CHANT_001-9a.6">《太平御覽》卷九百七十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
